Is this really happening in Zambia? An image shared on social media and attributed to Daimone Siulapwa depicts Zambian workers having lunch at a Chinese construction company. Zambia Reports is independently verifying the authenticity of the picture although all signs point to the fact that this is not a dream. It's happening in Zambia. Really? Daimone Siulapwa is Editor-in-Chief at the Voice Newspaper. Tell us what place this could be.